# ============================================================
# FILENOR: OPTIMIZE FORMATTER - GIT IGNORE CONFIGURATION
# ============================================================

### Python Basics ###
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so

### Virtual Environments ###
# Ignore local environment folders to keep the repo lightweight
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
bin/
lib/
include/

### Project Specific Binaries (CRITICAL) ###
# Large executables and portable folders must be kept locally
# Do not remove these from here to avoid hitting GitHub storage limits
ffmpeg.exe
LibreOffice/
*.exe
*.dll

### Build & Distribution ###
# Ignore folders created during the .exe creation process (PyInstaller/cx_Freeze)
build/
dist/
*.spec

### System Files ###
# OS generated files that add unnecessary noise to the repository
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

### User Specific & IDE Settings ###
# Local IDE configurations (VS Code, PyCharm)
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
